    "As examined earlier, the primary aim of the research is to assess the probability of a text being composed by AI.",
    "To accomplish this objective, pre-trained Transformer models were employed.",
    "Initially, pre-trained models were utilized without any finetuning.",
    "Following this, the models underwent fine-tuning to discern whether a scientific abstract was authored by an AI tool, relying on the distinctive writing styles inherent in both human and AI-generated content.",
    "When employing the standard version of Transformer models (i.e., without finetuning), the results of performance measures exhibit inconsistency, as detailed in Table 7."
  ]
}